item.description:
It's also my birthday so I thought what better way to have a relaxing day then to tire out my dog first!

Let's do the same hike as Saturday's... We'll meet at the Hickory Hill Drive trail entrance and go for an hour or so in a loop again.
item.how_to_find_us: Meet at the trail entrance under the power lines
